msgctxt "an4.118:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:0.2"
msgid "12. Kesivagga "
msgstr "12. With Kesi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.118:0.3"
msgid "118. Saṃvejanīyasutta "
msgstr "118. Inspiring "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.121, sc1
msgctxt "an4.118:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyāni saṃvejanīyāni ṭhānāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a faithful gentleman should go to see these four inspiring places. "

msgctxt "an4.118:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:1.3"
msgid "‘Idha tathāgato jāto’ti, bhikkhave, saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyaṃ saṃvejanīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘Here the Realized One was born!’—that is an inspiring place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:1.4"
msgid "‘Idha tathāgato anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti, bhikkhave, saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyaṃ saṃvejanīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘Here the Realized One became awakened as a supreme fully awakened Buddha!’—that is an inspiring place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:1.5"
msgid "‘Idha tathāgato anuttaraṃ dhammacakkaṃ pavattesī’ti, bhikkhave, saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyaṃ saṃvejanīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘Here the Realized One rolled forth the supreme Wheel of Dhamma!’—that is an inspiring place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:1.6"
msgid "‘Idha tathāgato anupādisesāya nibbānadhātuyā parinibbuto’ti, bhikkhave, saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyaṃ saṃvejanīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ. "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘Here the Realized One became fully extinguished through the natural principle of extinguishment, without anything left over!’—that is an inspiring place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.118:1.7"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri saddhassa kulaputtassa dassanīyāni saṃvejanīyāni ṭhānānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four inspiring places that a faithful gentleman should go to see.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.118:1.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

